{"tid":29910,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"鹿兒島岩唔岩一家大細去？","createTime":"2016-12-09T01:32:21.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-09T07:46:07.000Z","uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"19d5c8b040641ca03399ebaf300393517d26f06c","tid":29910,"uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:32:21.000Z","msg":"遲下復活節諗住同屋企去旅行，6大1小。<br />\n<br />\n肯定去日本架啦，沖繩兩老就去過，話想去未去過既鹿兒島。<br />\n<br />\n但上網睇唔多覺有人去，飛機都係得hk airline 有直飛。<br />\n<br />\n我最怕係冇咩玩，因為都諗住去5日4夜。有冇巴絲去過可以分享下？如果唔係我諗下去唔去墻沖繩算<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8abb0da9ab72bd37f0d75e728ad0f7e2648fcbde","tid":29910,"uid":42586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:42:54.000Z","msg":"自駕遊 啱<br />\n冇車唔好去  好多地方唔方便<br />\n老人家鍾意食野睇景的話會好啱玩"},{"pid":"5c2e959cc7d2c960eb1547aeba32df2ec0cf8d97","tid":29910,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:43:20.000Z","msg":"個次我又係同老人家 仲有一堆小朋友去<br />\n一日去左水族館 <br />\n天文館行街<br />\n有一日搭船去左櫻島<br />\n有一日去左動物園<br />\n<br />\n但我地係自駕遊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c54f9abdafed9f306740e3194d21396d106beebf","tid":29910,"uid":24775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:43:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>自駕遊 啱<br />\n冇車唔好去  好多地方唔方便<br />\n老人家鍾意食野睇景的話會好啱玩</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係 自駕遊就幾方便"},{"pid":"462cfa0b63906a133ac52db1c47a618deaeb1bf0","tid":29910,"uid":58091,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T01:46:32.000Z","msg":"岩岩十月去左3日鹿兒島<br />\n如果淨係鹿兒島市加櫻島2日都夠晒<br />\n但通常都會去埋指宿<br />\n睇景浸溫泉多<br />\n小朋友都有水族館睇下<br />\n你時間夠可以自駕去埋日南 宮崎<br />\n南九州係好休閒 但景點同沖繩一樣好唔集中<br />\n除左hx有飛uo都有飛<br />\n所以果到係超多香港人<br />\n天文館 櫻島 指宿超大部份都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db6a50f0333fcaa338254344e5dc5b183d98aea8","tid":29910,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T04:52:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>岩岩十月去左3日鹿兒島<br />\n如果淨係鹿兒島市加櫻島2日都夠晒<br />\n但通常都會去埋指宿<br />\n睇景浸溫泉多<br />\n小朋友都有水族館睇下<br />\n你時間夠可以自駕去埋日南 宮崎<br />\n南九州係好休閒 但景點同沖繩一樣好唔集中<br />\n除左hx有飛uo都有飛<br />\n所以果到係超多香港人<br />\n天文館 櫻島 指宿超大部份都係香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n基本上南九洲既外地客多數香港人其次大陸人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n宮崎鹿兒島櫻島霧島都撞到唔少香港人<br />\n除左有1日遊火車河去人吉就真係冇香港人"},{"pid":"29350accff97e140e1cbe8729230daf5e4ee01d5","tid":29910,"uid":1009,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:35:34.000Z","msg":"想問下樓上既手足，指宿溫泉酒店邊間好推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  上網睇吟松好似幾好，有無手足講下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f1dc6daa8efafc5291ca990f1d702fd3321fd14","tid":29910,"uid":2237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:41:57.000Z","msg":"我覺得去櫻島玩一日都唔錯呀<br />\n指宿個邊浸下溫泉，睇下景，食下流水麵又一日<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/N4iG451.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FN4iG451.jpg&h=1e0d3fd9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"884e8a2f88e7a9d3723aa87faada18c27ca0d3a3","tid":29910,"uid":50976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T05:54:06.000Z","msg":"櫻島玩到一日咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得幾個瞭望台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"067bdb0e141f86397b9df93978d2d7e1807f2372","tid":29910,"uid":4635,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:07:29.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>櫻島玩到一日咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 得幾個瞭望台<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n下面仲有博物館<br />\n唔係坐觀光巴士, 好似可以再去遠D<br />\n慢慢行起碼都可以玩大半日"},{"pid":"f1b0a1b0d79890aaf1397c861e1202a6ac2346f8","tid":29910,"uid":7796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"Hkexpress 都有直航"},{"pid":"84d83f13dea4845ef43363f0256d4c7c4f0101e8","tid":29910,"uid":18768,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T06:54:04.000Z","msg":"多謝大家意見，睇黎三日都玩得晒😭諗下轉唔轉好先"},{"pid":"cc68fd367fbc604b185e3a1b410760de0710cf5e","tid":29910,"uid":44263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-09T07:46:07.000Z","msg":"不如去北九州？<br />\n可以去埋大分 別府 熊本 阿蘇<br />\n有小朋友可以上aso farmland<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}